# Sales Data Deep-Dive Analysis & Interactive Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes a sales dataset using Python and presents insights through an interactive Streamlit dashboard.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Streamlit
- Plotly
- OpenPyXL

## Features
- KPI Cards
- Sales by Category
- Sales by City
- Monthly Sales Trend
- Top Selling Products
- Customer Segmentation
- Interactive Filters

## KPIs
- Total Sales
- Total Orders
- Total Customers
- Average Sales

## Deep-Dive Analysis
Customer Segmentation was performed by grouping customers into High Value, Medium Value, and Low Value segments based on total sales.

## How to Run

```bash
python -m streamlit run app.py
```
